      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING LIPA (5) is yet to miss the placings here in an excellent record which boasts four wins and two placings. Was out of placings last time (26.16) at Q Lakeside in a Grade 4/5, finishing eighth and beaten 11 lengths. Looks suited and should go close. ARNIE FERRARI (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when seventh at Q Straight over 350m behind Black Horse (19.73) in a Grade 3/4. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. SHINE A LIGHT (4) boasts a strong record this course with four wins and five minors from 11 tries. Hit the frame latest (19.73) when second at this track in a Grade 3/4. Looks well placed here and among the chances. KENNY DUTTON (2) is a surprise last-start placegetter who should be thereabouts.",
